Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.97,0:24:31.52,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}What's wrong, Takumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.52,0:24:36.10,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been racing because\Nthe situation called for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.10,0:24:40.14,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,This time, I feel like\Nit's a little different.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.72,0:24:44.53,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so excited, but I don't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.21,0:24:48.60,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fun and interesting to drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.21,0:24:54.76,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24}Anyway, I don't know how much I can do,\Nbut I want to try my best...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.96,0:24:52.57,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}He's different from the usual Takumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.57,0:24:54.46,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}Takumi is hyped up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.76,0:24:58.21,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}Next time on Initial D:\N"Last Great Battle!"
