Dialogue: 1,0:24:55.07,0:24:59.83,MainStyle,,0000,0430,0260,,Next Time:
Dialogue: 1,0:24:55.07,0:24:59.83,MainStyle,,0000,0110,0190,,Last Great Battle
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.21,0:24:59.46,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}Don't miss it!